title: Put God First In Your Life | Victoria Osteen
itunes:title: Put God First In Your Life | Victoria Osteen
description:
Don't let the busyness of life keep you from your purpose. When you let go of the distractions and prioritize spending time with God, He will crown your efforts with success!

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
